{"word":"ἔπειμι","slug":"ἔπειμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἔπειμι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἶμι\">εἶμι</a></el>; ‘come upon/near’] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> mostly as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fem.\">fem.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ptc.\">ptc.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπιοῦσα\">ἐπιοῦσα</a></el> <b>next,</b> referring to the following day, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> or without <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρα</a></el> <b><a href='B:510 7:26'>Ac 7:26</a>; <a href='B:510 16:11'>16:11</a>; <a href='B:510 20:15'>20:15</a>; <a href='B:510 21:18'>21:18</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νύξ\">νύξ</a></el> <b><a href='B:510 23:11'>23:11</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπεῖδον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπείπερ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}